        "## **Project Summary**\n",
        "\n",
        "This project develops an **Agentic AI-based Travel Planning Assistant** that functions like a smart virtual travel expert. The system uses structured datasets for flights, hotels, and tourist attractions along with a real-time weather API to automatically plan an optimized trip for users.\n",
        "\n",
        "Key components implemented include:\n",
        "- Flight Selection Tool to find the most cost-effective flights  \n",
        "- Hotel Recommendation Tool to suggest budget-friendly yet quality accommodation  \n",
        "- Tourist Places Tool to identify highly rated attractions  \n",
        "- Weather Tool using Open-Meteo API for live environmental insights  \n",
        "- Budget Estimation Tool for financial planning  \n",
        "\n",
        "All components are coordinated using a central **Main Travel Agent Function**, which performs data validation, executes decision logic, generates a day-wise travel itinerary, and compiles a complete travel plan.\n",
        "\n",
        "The final system outputs:\n",
        "- Best flight recommendation  \n",
        "- Optimal hotel suggestion with stay cost  \n",
        "- Top attractions list  \n",
        "- Weather forecast  \n",
        "- Day-wise itinerary  \n",
        "- Total estimated budget  \n",
        "\n",
        "This project showcases how AI automation can simplify real-world travel planning by combining data processing, reasoning, and decision-making into a single intelligent solution."
