        "## **Problem Statement**\n",
        "\n",
        "Planning a trip often requires users to manually search across multiple platforms for flights, hotels, tourist attractions, weather information, and cost estimates. This process is time-consuming, fragmented, and prone to poor decision-making due to scattered information and lack of automation.\n",
        "\n",
        "There is a need for an intelligent system that can consolidate data, reason over multiple parameters, and generate a complete end-to-end travel plan.  \n",
        "\n",
        "The challenge addressed in this project is:\n",
