        "**“How can we build an AI-powered Travel Planning Assistant that autonomously selects the best flights, recommends suitable hotels, suggests top tourist attractions, checks real-time weather, generates a structured itinerary, and estimates the total travel cost in a single automated workflow?”**\n",
