        "### **3. Weather Tool**\n",
        "\n",
        "Integrated real-time weather information to support smarter travel decisions.\n",
        "\n",
        "- Connected to the **Open-Meteo API**\n",
        "- Accepted latitude and longitude inputs for destination\n",
        "- Extracted daily maximum temperature forecasts\n",
        "- Returned clean, interpretable weather output\n",
        "\n",
        "Helps travelers prepare based on real weather expectations.\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "x71ZqKXriCWQ"
