    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# 3. WEATHER TOOL\n",
        "def get_weather(lat, lon):\n",
        "    url = f\"https://api.open-meteo.com/v1/forecast?latitude={lat}&longitude={lon}&daily=temperature_2m_max&timezone=auto\"\n",
        "    res = requests.get(url).json()\n",
        "    return {\n",
        "        \"date\": res[\"daily\"][\"time\"][0],\n",
        "        \"max_temp\": res[\"daily\"][\"temperature_2m_max\"][0]\n",
        "    }\n",
        "\n",
        "print(\"Weather System Ready \")\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "LWNFOSvLl09H"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "### **4. Flight Tool**\n",
        "\n",
        "Developed a flight selection engine to identify the best travel options.\n",
        "\n",
        "- Converted flight data into a DataFrame\n",
        "- Filtered flights by source and destination\n",
        "- Ensured pricing fields are numeric and comparable\n",
        "- Selected the most cost-effective flight option\n",
        "- Returned structured and user-friendly flight details\n",
        "\n",
        "Guarantees affordable and relevant flight recommendations."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "K4uUKy7Msjf8"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# 4. FLIGHT TOOL\n",
        "\n",
        "def find_best_flight(source, destination):\n",
        "    df = pd.DataFrame(flights)\n",
        "\n",
        "    df = df[\n",
        "        (df[\"from\"].str.lower() == source.lower()) &\n",
        "        (df[\"to\"].str.lower() == destination.lower())\n",
        "    ]\n",
        "\n",
        "    if df.empty:\n",
        "        return {\"message\": \"No flights found for this route\"}\n",
        "\n",
        "    df[\"price\"] = df[\"price\"].astype(int)\n",
        "\n",
        "    best = df.sort_values(by=\"price\").iloc[0]\n",
        "\n",
        "    return {\n",
        "        \"flight_id\": best[\"flight_id\"],\n",
        "        \"airline\": best[\"airline\"],\n",
        "        \"from\": best[\"from\"],\n",
        "        \"to\": best[\"to\"],\n",
        "        \"departure_time\": best[\"departure_time\"],\n",
        "        \"arrival_time\": best[\"arrival_time\"],\n",
        "        \"price\": int(best[\"price\"])\n",
        "    }\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "yQh9geKDs6qm"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "### **5. Hotel Tool**\n",
        "\n",
        "Implemented a hotel recommendation system balancing quality and budget.\n",
        "\n",
        "- Filtered hotels based on destination city\n",
        "- Ensured price fields are numeric\n",
        "- Calculated total stay cost using trip duration and number of travelers\n",
        "- Ranked hotels using star rating and price efficiency\n",
        "- Returned best hotel with amenities and complete cost summary\n",
        "\n",
        "Helps travelers stay comfortably without exceeding budget."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "h1EGLwPg557Z"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# 5. HOTEL TOOL\n",
        "\n",
        "def find_best_hotel(city, days, travelers):\n",
        "    df = pd.DataFrame(hotels)\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Filter hotels in destination city\n",
        "    df = df[df[\"city\"].str.lower() == city.lower()]\n",
        "\n",
        "    if df.empty:\n",
        "        return {\"message\": f\"No hotels found in {city}\"}\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Ensure prices are numeric\n",
        "    df[\"price_per_night\"] = df[\"price_per_night\"].astype(int)\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Calculate total cost\n",
        "    df[\"total_cost\"] = df[\"price_per_night\"] * days * travelers\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Pick best blend (cheapest but good rating)\n",
        "    df = df.sort_values(by=[\"stars\", \"price_per_night\"], ascending=[False, True])\n",
        "\n",
        "    best = df.iloc[0]\n",
        "\n",
        "    return {\n",
        "        \"hotel_id\": best[\"hotel_id\"],\n",
        "        \"name\": best[\"name\"],\n",
        "        \"city\": best[\"city\"],\n",
        "        \"stars\": int(best[\"stars\"]),\n",
        "        \"price_per_night\": int(best[\"price_per_night\"]),\n",
        "        \"amenities\": list(best[\"amenities\"]),\n",
        "        \"total_trip_cost\": int(best[\"total_cost\"])\n",
        "    }\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "qrjbT35bliKv"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "### **6. Places Tool**\n",
        "\n",
        "Built a tourist attraction suggestion feature to enhance trip experience.\n",
        "\n",
        "- Filtered attractions based on destination city\n",
        "- Sorted locations by highest ratings\n",
        "- Selected top recommended places\n",
        "- Returned structured attraction details\n",
        "\n",
        "Ensures travelers can explore the best highlights of their destination.\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
