      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# 6. PLACES TOOL\n",
        "\n",
        "def get_places(city, limit=5):\n",
        "    df = pd.DataFrame(places)\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Filter by destination city\n",
        "    df = df[df[\"city\"].str.lower() == city.lower()]\n",
        "\n",
        "    if df.empty:\n",
        "        return {\"message\": f\"No tourist places found in {city}\"}\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Sort highest rating → lowest\n",
        "    df = df.sort_values(by=\"rating\", ascending=False)\n",
        "\n",
        "    return df.head(limit).to_dict(orient=\"records\")\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "FEqg1n7frvJQ"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "### **7. Budget Tool**\n",
        "\n",
        "Estimated total trip expenditure to support financial planning.\n",
        "\n",
        "- Considered flight expenses\n",
        "- Calculated hotel stay cost\n",
        "- Added additional daily allowance for food and activities\n",
        "- Produced total estimated trip budget\n",
        "\n",
        "Helps users plan trips confidently with cost awareness."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Rdlrm8oZcKDS"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# 7. BUDGET TOOL\n",
        "def estimate_budget(flight_price, hotel_price, days):\n",
        "    hotel_total = hotel_price * days\n",
        "    misc = 1500 * days  # food + transport\n",
        "    return flight_price + hotel_total + misc\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "Z1NOAyO-l1Ki"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "### **8. Main Travel Agent Function**\n",
        "\n",
        "Designed the central intelligence system that powers the travel assistant.\n",
        "\n",
        "- Executed all supporting tools (flight, hotel, places, weather)\n",
        "- Validated and handled missing or unavailable data\n",
        "- Generated structured day-wise itinerary\n",
        "- Combined all components into a final trip plan\n",
        "- Calculated and returned total estimated budget\n",
        "\n",
        "Acts as the decision engine and delivers a complete AI-generated travel solution."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "OzPh8PqpcMUR"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "# 8. MAIN AGENT FUNCTION\n",
        "\n",
        "def travel_agent(name, source, destination, days, travelers, latitude, longitude):\n",
        "\n",
        "    print(\"Fetching best flight...\")\n",
        "    flight = find_best_flight(source, destination)\n",
        "\n",
        "    print(\"Selecting best hotel...\")\n",
        "    hotel = find_best_hotel(destination, days, travelers)\n",
        "\n",
        "    print(\"Finding top places to visit...\")\n",
        "    itinerary_places = get_places(destination)\n",
        "\n",
        "    print(\"Fetching weather...\")\n",
        "    weather = get_weather(latitude, longitude)\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Safety Checks\n",
        "    if not flight or \"message\" in flight:\n",
        "        return {\"error\": \"No suitable flights found.\"}\n",
        "\n",
        "    if not hotel or \"message\" in hotel:\n",
        "        return {\"error\": \"No suitable hotels found.\"}\n",
        "\n",
        "    if isinstance(itinerary_places, dict) and \"message\" in itinerary_places:\n",
        "        itinerary_places = []\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Simple Day-wise Itinerary\n",
        "    plan = []\n",
        "    if itinerary_places:\n",
        "        places_cycle = [p['name'] for p in itinerary_places]\n",
        "        for i in range(days):\n",
        "            place = places_cycle[i % len(places_cycle)]\n",
        "            plan.append(f\"Day {i+1}: Visit {place}\")\n",
        "    else:\n",
        "        for i in range(days):\n",
        "            plan.append(f\"Day {i+1}: Explore local attractions\")\n",
        "\n",
        "    # Budget\n",
        "    total_budget = flight[\"price\"] + hotel[\"total_trip_cost\"] + (1500 * days)\n",
        "\n",
        "    return {\n",
        "        \"Traveler\": name,\n",
        "        \"From\": source,\n",
        "        \"To\": destination,\n",
        "        \"Days\": days,\n",
        "        \"Travelers\": travelers,\n",
        "        \"Weather Forecast\": f\"{weather['max_temp']}°C expected\",\n",
        "        \"Flight Selected\": flight,\n",
        "        \"Hotel Selected\": hotel,\n",
        "        \"Itinerary\": plan,\n",
        "        \"Estimated Budget\": f\"₹{total_budget}\"\n",
        "    }\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "tTG-ogc6rgit"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
